title: Feature/pipeline
body:
This PR allows to automate CI for this library:
1. prepare (check libraries, download iroha)
2. geneate Schema using protoc
3. (optional) If there is `master` tree and it was tagged, automatically push cocoa pod to https://cocoapods.org/pods/IrohaCommunication 

```
brew install protobuf c-ares
git clone --depth 1 https://github.com/grpc/grpc/
cd grpc
make grpc_objective_c_plugin
cp bins/opt/grpc_objective_c_plugin /usr/local/bin/protoc-gen-objcgrpc
```
